  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Prevent Suicide &amp; Homophobic Bullying in Chile</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Chile has the highest rates of teen suicide in Latin America and some of the highest levels of school violence.  Kids who are or appear to be lesbian, gay, bi or trans are among the most vulnerable to discrimination and at higher risks of self harm. Todo Mejora works to save lives! We develop programs in vulnerable schools that promote diversity, safe spaces, and prevent homophobic bullying. With funds from this campaign, we will reach 2,000+ students 10-18, teachers &amp; school principals.</narrative>
  </description>
